y, I think I have enough to write a comprehensive review. Let me summarize the i
ssues I've found:\n\n**Critical issues:**\n1. **Mobile pubspec missing `social_w
orld_profile_models` dependency**: `apps/mobile/pubspec.yaml` references `social
