male, all]` but DTOs have `[male, female, both, all]`.\n3. **Redundant DB column
**: `user_profiles.photo_urls` was added via migration and exists in entity, but
the application uses `user_photos` table instead. This creates inconsistency.\n\
n**Medium issues:**\n4. **Widgetbook missing SwBottomSheet**: The execution plan
step 0.2 says all new components must be registered in widgetbook. `SwBottomShee
t` is missing.\n5. **Profile BDD step definitions are no-ops**: While they techn
ically bind via `autoBindSteps` using `common.js`, all profile-specific steps in
