is means BDD tests pass but provide no real coverage.\n6. **No unit tests for Pr
ofileService**: Only `age-calculator.spec.ts` exists, but `profile.service.ts` h
as no tests despite having complex business logic (photo limits, reordering, age
validation, etc.).\n7. **Scope creep - Matching and IM in Profile PR**: The PR i
ncludes full matching and IM module implementations. While not strictly a bug, t
his violates the principle of focused PRs and makes review difficult. However, s
ince these modules are actually needed for the ProfileCompletionGuard integratio
